description:
This layer shows the distribution of human population within the WIO countries.
Gridded Human Population count (global) 2015 estimate data was used to derive WIO national human population grids. The grids are derived at 1 Km spatial resolution.
keywords: human, population, Africa, East Africa, Kenya, Madagascar, Mauritius, Mayotte, Mozambique, Reunion, Seychelles, Somalia, United Republic of Tanzania, Southern Africa, South Africa
name: National human population count in the WIO
